Interface SequencePullStreamer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FrequencyPullStreamer, SequencePointerPullStreamer, SequencePullStreamerDecorator, SimpleSequencePullStreamer

    public interface SequencePullStreamer
    Object that work on sequences. The pull(String, Object...) method has to be used inside the SequenceStreamer.stream() method in order to "pull" informations about each sequence streamed.
    Author:
    Giovanni Bacci
